  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到珀炼市，秘知使大人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《协律01：新生活》是一款幻想都市生活RPG游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以一块废弃基地为起点：耕作，制造、冒险和探索，享受丰富多彩的社交生活！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/0d09b5fbddea0444b040110781a1a4e3.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索精心设计的都市舞台，挖掘剧情谜团与街坊故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/2d68ad7f7013d99a344f876fc485ec54.poster.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/2d68ad7f7013d99a344f876fc485ec54.webm?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/2d68ad7f7013d99a344f876fc485ec54.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/66dacb3b2b03e3d65b492aaaed14bcb8.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邂逅8位特殊角色，谁将是你缔结心之誓约的羁绊？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城市中还生活着许多个性居民，众生芸芸却不平凡，打开每一个人的独特心扉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/905700b994998c93bb186bf7933ca522.poster.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/905700b994998c93bb186bf7933ca522.webm?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/905700b994998c93bb186bf7933ca522.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/52224ec41cd3b27d7ea10384e5d32fbe.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中最重要的活动——“城市复兴大赛”！这场数年一度的大竞赛，旨在选拔文明重建的年轻英才。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赛中包含“生产、建设、环保、治安、文化”等多种生活课题，寻觅、集结和游说城市中的各类英才，一起赢下比赛吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/b04510ebcdb522d17ba29093c36adef6.poster.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/b04510ebcdb522d17ba29093c36adef6.webm?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/b04510ebcdb522d17ba29093c36adef6.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天灾中幸存的后末日城市，依然处处物资短缺，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将都市边缘的废弃工厂改造为生产基地，耕作、制造、探险，勤劳致富从此开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/cc5dc4a05d9242be2482ae31cf2cb6c1.poster.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/cc5dc4a05d9242be2482ae31cf2cb6c1.webm?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/cc5dc4a05d9242be2482ae31cf2cb6c1.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/6bbe2e8bde56138a091bf94f30fcd086.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种多样的街区活动，深入细节的生活体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/cb2eff41d9db4d19bf9fab59429ac937.poster.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/cb2eff41d9db4d19bf9fab59429ac937.webm?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/cb2eff41d9db4d19bf9fab59429ac937.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/e97b2361c91394202af4856940f070e9.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富多彩的换装系统，成为珀炼城的时尚先锋吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/19afc41d7383d7fb0e9f985def36c50b.poster.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/19afc41d7383d7fb0e9f985def36c50b.webm?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/19afc41d7383d7fb0e9f985def36c50b.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装饰私有基地，打造生机盎然的温馨家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/52a3781a364eeefb56cdaa99ad9bc1ed.poster.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/52a3781a364eeefb56cdaa99ad9bc1ed.webm?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/52a3781a364eeefb56cdaa99ad9bc1ed.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/a971240a8f987ce6b15ac73f53b24075.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破解重重机关，探索无人深处，用力量与智慧化解危机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/c3e0f82b86f4b7a43c2c09089a2ec897.poster.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/c3e0f82b86f4b7a43c2c09089a2ec897.webm?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/c3e0f82b86f4b7a43c2c09089a2ec897.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
