fc41d7383d7fb0e9f985def36c50b.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装饰私有基地，打造生机盎然的温馨家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/52a3781a364eeefb56cdaa99ad9bc1ed.poster.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/52a3781a364eeefb56cdaa99ad9bc1ed.webm?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/52a3781a364eeefb56cdaa99ad9bc1ed.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/a971240a8f987ce6b15ac73f53b24075.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破解重重机关，探索无人深处，用力量与智慧化解危机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/c3e0f82b86f4b7a43c2c09089a2ec897.poster.avif?t=1764223331\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/c3e0f82b86f4b7a43c2c09089a2ec897.webm?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730530/extras/c3e0f82b86f4b7a43c2c09089a2ec897.mp4?t=1764223331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
